div.p:
              Anſw. Time permits not to inſtruct and direct fully in this;

I muſt therefore ſend you to that whole armour of God, mentioned in Epheſ. 6. 11. to 13. and doe beſeech you to ſtudy that; 

                    〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
                 . where you are directed what ſpirituall weapons you muſt get to fight with; as alſo, how wiſely, and with what ſpiritual skill theſe ought to be uſed in this warfare; and for the preſert doe but obſerve theſe generall directions, imitating a good ſouldier of Jeſus Chriſt; make ſuch a one your patterne in theſe foure 2 Tim. 2. 3. particulars.
